Use this to install twint on ubuntu:

pip3 install --upgrade -e git+https://github.com/twintproject/twint.git@origin/master#egg=twint

run the coins_scraper.py file to periodically scrape cmc for new tokens

run the mentions_scraper.py to scrape the mentions from various social networks and produce reports from the results

Run the data_enrichment.py file to update the sentiment and google score of the cryptocurrencies collected
